PrecisApproval of the reappointment by the Minister for International Trade of CHRISTA C. WESSEL of Oakville, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Commercial Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective July 1, 2020.
